[Dr. Crawford is among those whose research may indicate that this is
a case of equine influenza. If this is the case, it would be the 1st
time the equine flu may have crossed species barriers. This research
is ongoing and is still only suggestive.
More information regarding the crossing of the species barrier may be
found in DVM Magazine. The magazine carries an online article on Dr.
Crawford's research:
<http://www.dvmnewsmagazine.com/dvm/article/articleDetail.jsp?id=99227>
- Mod.TG]
